text: kar thveu dauchnaoh kuchea kar thveusaeaksaei del chit tow rk pheap troemotrauv cheangke ryy puokke phyokhlach ke nung bdeseth nung samboth banteab pi kar sbath robsa puokke . haey chaur puok anak kaotakhlach a l laoh ning stab( dambaunman robsa trong) . haey a l laoh min changaoulobangheanh dl krom del lmeusa nung chbab robsa a l laoh laey
